=====Usage notes=====
* ''Nippon'' is the official reading of {{m|ja|日本}}, although ''Nihon'' is also acknowledged.
* In everyday conversation, ''Nihon'' is more common. <!--https://www.nhk.or.jp/bunken/summary/kotoba/research/002.html-->
* Politically, ''Nippon'' appears to be correlated with right-wing groups, and ''Nihon'' with left-wing groups.<!-- Citation? -->

